aVfirst decoded this beautiful double helix that we know as the DNA molecule \u2014
p53
aVvery long, complicated molecule \u2014
p54
aVwe then started on this journey to understand that
p55
aVinside of that DNA is a language that determines the characteristics, our traits,
p56
aVwhat we inherit, what diseases we may get.
