aa(lp192
VSo, what can we do with genomes now that we can read them,
p193
aVnow that we're starting to have the book of life?
p194
aVWell, there's many things. Some are exciting.
p195
aVSome people will find very scary. I will tell you a couple of things
p196
aVthat will probably make you want to projectile puke on me, but that's okay.
p197
aVSo, you know, we now can learn the history of organisms.
p198
